query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(lt ml cc) NoMergeJoin(cc lt ml t) NoNestLoop(cc lt ml t cct1) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 lt ml t cct2) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 lt ml t mk) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 lt mk ml t k) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 cn k lt mc mi mk ml t ct) */ select min(cn.name) AS producing_company,
min(lt.link) AS link_type,
min(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
from link_type AS lt
inner join movie_link AS ml
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link like '%follow%'
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join title AS t
on ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2010
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind like 'complete%'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = t.id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Norway',
'Germany',
'Denmark',
'Swedish',
'Denish',
'Norwegian',
'German',
'English')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND ( cn.name like '%Film%' OR cn.name like '%Warner%')
inner join company_type AS ct
on mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies';
